  abstract={Cluster formation operation is the primary operation mode and means to win the future war, especially the air force cluster operation. Therefore, based on the background of air force operations, this paper focuses on the analysis of cluster operation technology using OODA ring, cluster formation flight control, cooperative route planning and replanning technology, formation task allocation technology, cluster formation reconstruction technology, collaborative operation technology, distributed operation management technology, multi-source data analysis and fusion technology, intelligent unmanned system, agile command and control technology, etc. In this paper, we perform an analysis of the current research status and future development trends to provide a reference for the research of cluster formation operations.},
